
'''''Platoon Leader''''' ni film ya Cannon Films yo mu 1988 yakozwe mu ntambara ya Vietnam kandi iyobowe na Aaron Norris<ref>https://www.cinemaretro.com/index.php?/archives/11143-REVIEW-PLATOON-LEADER-1988-AND-SOLDIER-BOYZ-1995;-MICHAEL-DUDIKOFF-BLU-RAY-DOUBLE-FEATURE.html</ref>; ikinamo Michael Dudikoff na Michael DeLorenzo kandi yafatiwe amashusho muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo. Rishingiye ku nyandiko ya James R. McDonough yibuka izina rimwe<ref>https://www.kinolorber.com/film/view/id/3000</ref>. Iyi filime ivuga kubyerekeranye na liyetona mushya [[Viyetinamu|w’abasirikare bageze muri Vietnam]] kugira ngo yigarurire platoni ye ya mbere<ref>http://www.imfdb.org/wiki/Platoon_Leader</ref>. Asanga agomba kwigaragaza no kugirirwa ikizere nabagabo banditswe niba ashaka kubayobora<ref>https://en-academic.com/dic.nsf/enwiki/2642213</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Lt. Jeffrey Knight, umusirikare mushya wo mu Ishuri rya Gisirikare rya Leta zunze ubumwe za [[Amerika]],<ref>https://mubi.com/films/platoon-leader</ref> yajyanywe mu ndege ku birindiro biri muri Vietnam, aho ahurira na platon  ye, itsinda ry’abasirikare bakomeye b'intambara<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/film562151.html</ref>. Platon Serija McNamara asobanurira Knight ko platoni idakeneye umuyobozi ukurikiza amategeko. Ibikorwa bya Lt. Knight nabyo byamaganwa nabagabo be bose usibye Pvt. Parker, umukoresha wa radio<ref>https://www.britannica.com/topic/Platoon-film-by-Stone</ref>.

Kuri rimwe mu irondo rye rya mbere, Knight yasitaye atitaye ku kirombe cyanjye cy'urugendo kandi aricwa. Parker noneho amaradiyo ya evac hanyuma McNamara ategeka ingabo kwimukira muri LZ kugirango zivemo<ref>https://www.senscritique.com/film/Platoon_Leader/477399</ref> . Nyuma, mu gihe Lt. Knight arimo gukira ibikomere mu bitaro bya Gisirikare, Major Flynn amubaza niba ashobora kongera gufata icyemezo maze Knight arabyemera<ref>https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1988-10-07-ca-3320-story.html</ref>. Knight asubizwa mu ndege asubira ku birindiro bya platon ariko ntiyakirwa n'abantu be asanga ibikoresho bye byabuze aho yari atuye, kuko batari biteze ko azagaruka<ref>https://www.undertheradarmag.com/reviews/platoon_leader_soldier_boyz_michael_dudikoff_double_feature</ref>. Bamenye ko Knight yagarutse, abasirikare bihutira gusubiza ibintu bye hanze y'ibiro bye mbere yuko agaruka. Knight amenya ko agomba gufata ubundi buryo kugirango abagabo be bamwubahe<ref>https://vodkaster.telerama.fr/films/platoon-leader/1289739</ref>.

